725718f-a.title: Queens: 93rd Avenue - 170th Street
725718f-a.text:
93rd Avenue (right), at the N.E. corner of 170th Street.
These two old homes were owned by T. Bell and T. Klin in
1873.
P. L. Sperr  April 1, 1932
